                           HOW IT WORKS

After receiving shareware fee we will send you a keyfail via e-mail or
snail mail.

To turn your unregistered version of CyberBlast 2 into a registered
version, you only have to copy the keyfile to the volume CYBER in drawer
KeyFile

Please do not redistribute the keyfile or registered, unlaced version of
the game. Such distribution is Piracy. If we came across such a game
we can always trace it beck to you using the keyfile.

