                           HERE IS HOW TO ORDER

Now that you decided to order Cyber Blast 2. There is one way to do it:

  Cash:
 The shareware fee is

        5 $  (US-Dollars) or equivalent in your country's currency

              REMEMBER: DO NOT SEND COINS ONLY PAPER MONEY

Place the money in the envelope in a way it can't be seen from the outside.
Send a filled-out OrderForm with the cash.


The Order Form is on the disk Cyber in the text format.
Important:

REMEMBER WE WILL ONLY SEND YOU A KEY FILE WHEN WE RECIVE PAYMENT

IF YOU WANT TO GET THE KEYFILE VIA SLOW-MAIL ALWAYS SEND A 3.5" DISK


